  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  OAHI &gt;= 2

          -  Tonsillary hypertrophy, Brodsky size 2-4

          -  Adequate swedish knowledge

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiovascular disorders

          -  Pulmonary disorders

          -  Neuromuscular disorders

          -  Cranoifacial malformations

          -  Genetic disorders

          -  Obesity

          -  Earlier performed adenoid-tonsillary-surgery

          -  Bleeding disorders
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
